### ১.৩ কম্পোনেন্ট-ভিত্তিক বিশ্লেষণ

---

#### IslamicCard — [components/IslamicCard.tsx](file:///home/shazol/antigravaty%20plus%20kiro/41%20Smoke-free-path/smoke-free-path/components/IslamicCard.tsx)

- **Bookmark বাটন:** `onBookmark` undefined হলেও `TouchableOpacity` render হয় — তাতে tap করলে কিছু হয় না, confusing
- **Accessibility:** Card-level `accessibilityLabel` নেই — screen reader user কন্টেন্ট বুঝতে পারে না
- **Type badge colors** hardcoded single palette — Dark Mode-এ যেকোনো `dua` type-এ (#6A1B9A) খুব dark হতে পারে

#### TriggerSelector — [components/TriggerSelector.tsx](file:///home/shazol/antigravaty%20plus%20kiro/41%20Smoke-free-path/smoke-free-path/components/TriggerSelector.tsx)

- **Hardcoded colors:** `borderColor: '#2E7D32'`, `backgroundColor: '#fff'` — Dark Mode-এ bright white chips
- **Deselection:** একবার select করলে deselect করার উপায় নেই — re-tap deselect করে না
- **Accessibility:** `accessibilityRole` ও `accessibilityState` নেই

#### CravingTimer — [components/CravingTimer.tsx](file:///home/shazol/antigravaty%20plus%20kiro/41%20Smoke-free-path/smoke-free-path/components/CravingTimer.tsx)

- Timer circle static (no animated ring) — visually boring
- `btnSecondary` (line 160): hardcoded `backgroundColor: '#F9A825'` — Dark Mode-এ theme-consistent নয়
- "বাতিল করুন" বাটন — confirmation ছাড়াই action trigger হয়

#### StepCard — [components/StepCard.tsx](file:///home/shazol/antigravaty%20plus%20kiro/41%20Smoke-free-path/smoke-free-path/components/StepCard.tsx)

- `STATUS_CONFIG` (line 12-27): সব colors hardcoded — theme-aware নয়
- Locked step (`'future'`): `backgroundColor: '#e0e0e0'`, `textColor: '#9e9e9e'` — Dark Mode-এ visible হবে না
- Card size (48×56) fixed — responsive নয়, বিভিন্ন device-এ UI break হতে পারে
- `accessibilityLabel` নেই — screen reader users `step 1, complete` type info পায় না

#### ProgressCalendar — [components/ProgressCalendar.tsx](file:///home/shazol/antigravaty%20plus%20kiro/41%20Smoke-free-path/smoke-free-path/components/ProgressCalendar.tsx)

- Cell size ৩৬×৩৬ — ছোট device-এ touch target (44px minimum) পূরণ হয় না
- Current step-এ hardcoded `backgroundColor: '#F9A825'`, `borderColor: '#E65100'`

#### HealthTimeline — [components/HealthTimeline.tsx](file:///home/shazol/antigravaty%20plus%20kiro/41%20Smoke-free-path/smoke-free-path/components/HealthTimeline.tsx)

- Timeline dots only — connecting line নেই, timeline visualization incomplete
- Achieved ও unachieved entries-র মধ্যে opacity difference নেই — all look similar

#### Tab Bar — [app/(tabs)/_layout.tsx](file:///home/shazol/antigravaty%20plus%20kiro/41%20Smoke-free-path/smoke-free-path/app/(tabs)/_layout.tsx)

- ৬টি tab — best practice সর্বোচ্চ ৫টি recommended (HIG/Material Design)
- Emoji icons instead of proper vector icons — platform inconsistency, rendering varies
- Tab labels `11px` — barely readable
- `paddingBottom: 4` — iOS-এ home indicator overlap হতে পারে

