## ২. বাগ ও এররস

### ২.১ Visual Bugs (UI Glitches)

| # | বাগ | ফাইল | লাইন | Priority |
|---|------|------|:----:|:--------:|
| B01 | **Dark Mode Color Crash:** Onboarding সব screen (`welcome.tsx`, `profile-setup.tsx`, `quit-date.tsx`) hardcoded light theme — Dark Mode-এ পুরো white/light green background থাকে | `app/(onboarding)/*.tsx` | — | 🔴 High |
| B02 | **হোম স্ক্রিন savings row:** Dark Mode-এ `#1B5E20` text, `#C8E6C9` border, `#A5D6A7` divider invisible | `app/(tabs)/index.tsx` | 350-379 | 🔴 High |
| B03 | **StepCard locked state:** `#e0e0e0` bg ও `#9e9e9e` text Dark Mode-এ contrast 1.1:1 — WCAG fail | `components/StepCard.tsx` | 12-28 | 🔴 High |
| B04 | **TriggerSelector chips:** `backgroundColor: '#fff'` Dark Mode-এ bright white flash | `components/TriggerSelector.tsx` | 52 | 🟡 Medium |
| B05 | **Intensity buttons:** `backgroundColor: '#fff'` Dark Mode-এ white circles on dark background | `app/craving/index.tsx` | 374 | 🟡 Medium |
| B06 | **Countdown banner:** `#E3F2FD` bg, `#1565C0` text hardcoded — Dark Mode incompatible | `app/(tabs)/tracker.tsx` | 207-222 | 🟡 Medium |
| B07 | **Future date card:** `#E3F2FD` bg hardcoded | `app/(tabs)/progress.tsx` | 367-376 | 🟡 Medium |
| B08 | **Motivation banner:** `#FFF8E1` bg, `#E65100` text hardcoded | `app/(tabs)/progress.tsx` | 377-390 | 🟡 Medium |
| B09 | **Alert card:** `#FFF3E0` bg hardcoded | `app/trigger-log/index.tsx` | 214-222 | 🟡 Medium |
| B10 | **IslamicSection special cards:** `insightCard`, `reflectionCard`, `ramadanCard`, `familyCard` সব hardcoded colors | `components/IslamicSection.tsx` | 140-258 | 🟡 Medium |

### ২.২ UX-Related Logical Errors

| # | সমস্যা | ফাইল | Priority |
|---|--------|------|:--------:|
| L01 | **Bookmark button renders even when `onBookmark` is undefined** — `TouchableOpacity` tap করলে কিছু হয় না | `components/IslamicCard.tsx` L68-70 | 🟡 Medium |
| L02 | **Submit button visually disabled but functionally active** — `submitBtnDisabled` style applied কিন্তু `disabled={!selectedTrigger}` prop নেই | `app/trigger-log/index.tsx` L171-173 | 🔴 High |
| L03 | **TriggerSelector no deselect** — user trigger select করলে deselect করতে পারে না | `components/TriggerSelector.tsx` L28 | 🟡 Medium |
| L04 | **Slip-up "continue" button no confirmation** — directly dispatches without asking | `app/slip-up/index.tsx` L119-126 | 🟡 Medium |
| L05 | **Notification time input raw text** — user ভুল format দিতে পারে; time picker UI নেই | `components/NotificationSettings.tsx` L72-97 | 🟡 Medium |
| L06 | **Onboarding no back navigation** — profile-setup ও quit-date-এ back button নেই | `app/(onboarding)/*.tsx` | 🟡 Medium |
| L07 | **ErrorBoundary uses `useTheme` inside ThemeProvider** — কিন্তু ErrorBoundary ThemeProvider-এর বাইরে wrapped — crash হলে theme পাওয়া যাবে না | `app/_layout.tsx` L89-95 | 🔴 High |

### ২.৩ Responsiveness / Cross-Device সমস্যা

| # | সমস্যা | ফাইল | Priority |
|---|--------|------|:--------:|
| R01 | **StepCard fixed 48×56px** — ছোট screen-এ 7 columns overflow হতে পারে | `components/StepCard.tsx` L58-59 | 🟡 Medium |
| R02 | **ProgressCalendar cell 36×36 fixed** — screen width vary করলে cell সঠিক fit হয় না | `components/ProgressCalendar.tsx` L107-109 | 🟡 Medium |
| R03 | **Intensity buttons 10টি fixed 40px width** — narrow screens-এ awkward wrap | `app/craving/index.tsx` L366-375 | 🟡 Medium |
| R04 | **Tab bar 6 tabs** — landscape mode-এ labels cut হতে পারে | `app/(tabs)/_layout.tsx` | 🟢 Low |
| R05 | **ScrollView nested in tab** — keyboard overlap issue possible on small devices | `app/(tabs)/settings.tsx` | 🟢 Low |

