### ৩.৩ Accessibility (a11y) উন্নতি

| # | সমস্যা | ফাইল | সমাধান |
|---|--------|------|--------|
| A01 | StepCard-এ `accessibilityLabel` নেই | `components/StepCard.tsx` | `accessibilityLabel={`ধাপ ${step}, ${status}`}` যোগ করুন |
| A02 | Tab bar emoji icons screen reader-এ meaningless | `app/(tabs)/_layout.tsx` | Proper `accessibilityLabel` per tab |
| A03 | Color-only status indication (StepCard, ProgressCalendar) | Multiple | Icon + color combination ব্যবহার করুন |
| A04 | IslamicCard Arabic text font selection | `components/IslamicCard.tsx` | `accessibilityLanguage="ar"` যোগ করুন |
| A05 | Timer progress no screen reader update | `components/CravingTimer.tsx` | `AccessibilityInfo.announceForAccessibility()` per minute |
| A06 | Contrast ratio WCAG AA fail | `StepCard` future state | Minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio নিশ্চিত করুন |
| A07 | Touch targets < 44px | `ProgressCalendar` cells | Minimum 44×44px maintain করুন |
| A08 | No `accessibilityRole="header"` on section titles | Multiple screens | যোগ করুন |
| A09 | Form inputs missing `accessibilityHint` | `profile-setup.tsx` | যেমন: "আপনার পুরো নাম লিখুন" |
| A10 | `ReduceMotion` check only Craving/SlipUp/TriggerLog-এ — অন্যান্য animation unchecked | `library.tsx`, `dua.tsx` AnimatedItems | সব animated components-এ check যোগ করুন |

