## ৫. A-grade মানের রেফারেন্স

### প্রতিটি সমস্যার বিপরীতে Industry Best Practice

---

#### 🎨 Color System ও Dark Mode

| সমস্যা | Best Practice | উদাহরণ App |
|--------|--------------|------------|
| Hardcoded colors | **Material Design 3 Dynamic Color System** — সকল color semantic token হিসেবে define করুন (`surface`, `onSurface`, `primary`, `onPrimary`, etc.) | Google Keep, Todoist |
| Dark Mode support partial | **Apple HIG:** "Every screen should work in both Light and Dark Mode" — `useColorScheme()` + theme context | Apple Health, Muslim Pro |
| Color-only status indication | **WCAG 2.1 SC 1.4.1:** "Color is not used as the only visual means" — icon + color + text label | Duolingo (✓ checkmark + green) |

#### 📝 Typography

| সমস্যা | Best Practice | উদাহরণ App |
|--------|--------------|------------|
| System default fonts | **Google Fonts integration** — Bengali: "Noto Sans Bengali" (body), "Hind Siliguri" (display) | BBC Bangla, Prothom Alo |
| Flat font hierarchy | **Type Scale System** — 5+ distinct sizes with clear hierarchy: Display (28+), Heading (22-24), Title (18-20), Body (14-16), Caption (11-12) | Material Design 3 |

#### 🧭 Navigation ও UX Flow

| সমস্যা | Best Practice | উদাহরণ App |
|--------|--------------|------------|
| ৬ tabs overcrowded | **Material Design:** "Bottom nav should have 3-5 destinations" — merge similar tabs | Instagram (5 tabs), WhatsApp (4 tabs) |
| Emoji tab icons | **Vector icon library** — consistent, scalable, customizable | Expo's `@expo/vector-icons` |
| No floating critical action | **FAB (Floating Action Button)** — persistent, accessible emergency action | Google Maps (directions FAB) |
| `Alert.alert()` for all feedback | **In-app Snackbar/Toast** — non-disruptive, auto-dismissable | YouTube (snackbar), Twitter/X (toast) |

#### 🎭 Animation ও Motion

| সমস্যা | Best Practice | উদাহরণ App |
|--------|--------------|------------|
| Static timer | **Animated circular progress** — `react-native-svg` Circle + animated stroke-dashoffset | Headspace (breathing animation) |
| No transition animations | **Shared Element Transitions** — `react-native-reanimated` | Apple Music (card expand) |
| No micro-interactions | **Spring animations on touch** — scale(0.95) press, opacity transitions | Airbnb (heart animation) |
| Milestone static emoji confetti | **Lottie animations** — rich, performant celebration animations | Duolingo (lesson complete) |

#### ♿ Accessibility

| সমস্যা | Best Practice | উদাহরণ App |
|--------|--------------|------------|
| Missing `accessibilityLabel` | **Every interactive element needs a label** — descriptive, concise | Apple Guidelines |
| Touch targets < 44px | **WCAG 2.5.5:** Minimum 44×44px touch target | Material Design (48dp minimum) |
| No `accessibilityRole` | **Proper roles:** `button`, `link`, `header`, `search`, `tab` | React Native docs |
| ReduceMotion partial | **Universal reduce-motion check** — wrap all animations in `ReduceMotion` guard | iOS Settings example |

#### 📐 Layout ও Spacing

| সমস্যা | Best Practice | উদাহরণ App |
|--------|--------------|------------|
| Fixed component sizes | **Responsive dimensions** — `useWindowDimensions()` + percentage-based sizing | Any modern RN app |
| Inconsistent padding | **8-point grid system** — all spacing multiples of 4/8: xs=4, sm=8, md=16, lg=24, xl=32 | ✅ Already defined in `theme.tsx` but underutilized |
| Information overload (Progress) | **Progressive disclosure** — collapsible sections, "Show more" patterns | Apple Health (daily/weekly/monthly tabs) |

---

